webResources.textAttributionSnippet: (en) The present church in Sund was completed in 1794 after nearly a hundred years of discussion of a new church room to accommodate the increased population. It was built on the foundations of an older, medieval church building. To its exterior, the church obtained a distinct Gustavian touch - https://www.europeana.eu/item/73/S_OM_photo_OMFB000297.
